 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. 프로젝트 생성</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\">gatsby new <span class=\"token variable\">${PROJECT_NAME}</span> https://github.com/gatsbyjs/gatsby-starter-hello-world</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"3-서버-실행-개발-모드\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-%EC%84%9C%EB%B2%84-%EC%8B%A4%ED%96%89-%EA%B0%9C%EB%B0%9C-%EB%AA%A8%EB%93%9C\" aria-label=\"3 서버 실행 개발 모드 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. 서버 실행 (개발 모드)</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\">gatsby develop</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>서버가 정상적으로 실행되면 <code class=\"language-text\">localhost:8000</code>로 접속 할 수 있다. <br/>\n또한 <code class=\"language-text\">localhost:8000/___graphql</code>로 접속하면 GraphiQL을 통해 GraphQL을 쉽게 작성 할 수 있다.</p>\n<!-- ## 기능 구현하기 -->\n<!-- ## 디렉토리 구조 -->\n<h2 id=\"참고\" style=